<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>Pablo Iranzo Gómez's blog - MiniKube</title><link>https://iranzo.io/</link><description>A bunch of unrelated data</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2019 21:16:14 +0200</lastBuildDate><item><title>Katacoda scenario creation</title><link>https://iranzo.io/blog/2019/06/11/katacoda-scenario-creation/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;After some time checking the scenarios at &lt;a href="https://learn.openshift.com"&gt;https://learn.openshift.com&lt;/a&gt;, I decided to give it a&amp;nbsp;try.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With the help of &lt;a href="https://linuxera.org"&gt;Mario Vázquez&lt;/a&gt;, author of &lt;a href="https://learn.openshift.com/introduction/federated-clusters/"&gt;Getting Started with Kubefed&lt;/a&gt;, I did create two&amp;nbsp;scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.katacoda.com/iranzo/scenarios/citellus"&gt;How to use Citellus&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href="https://citellusorg.github.io"&gt;Citellus: Troubleshooting&amp;nbsp;automation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.katacoda.com/iranzo/scenarios/kubevirt"&gt;KubeVirt&lt;/a&gt; on a &amp;#8216;browser-based&amp;#8217; approach for &lt;a href="https://kubevirt.io/quickstart_minikube/"&gt;MiniKube&lt;/a&gt; setup for validating KubeVirt: Kubernetes with &lt;span class="caps"&gt;VM&lt;/span&gt; Virtualization (versus the regular&amp;nbsp;containers).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can check how them can be created by looking at their code at: &lt;a href="https://github.com/iranzo/katacoda-scenarios"&gt;Katacoda Scenarios&lt;/a&gt; or the &amp;#8216;playable&amp;#8217; version at &lt;a href="https://www.katacoda.com/iranzo/"&gt;https://www.katacoda.com/iranzo/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Pablo Iranzo Gómez</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2019 21:16:14 +0200</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">tag:iranzo.io,2019-06-11:/blog/2019/06/11/katacoda-scenario-creation/</guid><category>tech</category><category>Linux</category><category>MiniKube</category><category>Citellus</category><category>Katacoda</category><category>FOSS</category><category>KubeVirt</category><category>Kubernetes</category><category>k8s</category></item></channel></rss>